\id MAL
\h Malaxi
\toc1 Malaxi
\toc2 Malaxi
\toc3 Mal.
\mt1 Malaxi
\c 1
\s1 Tayri n SIDI i Israil
\m 
\v 1 Řḥukm issaggʷaden. Awař n SIDI i Israil s ufus n Malaxi.
\b
\m 
\v 2 “Necc tuɣa ttexseɣ cek, iqqar SIDI, maca kenniw teqqarem: ‘Mani d aneɣ texsed?’ Ma war iǧi Ɛisu d umas n Yaɛqub, iqqar SIDI, u Necc ttexseɣ Yaɛqub, \x ◘ \xo 1:2 \xt Rum. 9:13\x*
\v 3 \add maca\add* carheɣ Ɛisu. Necc arriɣ idurar nnes d ict n temmurt ittwareddǧen uřa d tasɣart nnes i wuccanen n řexřa.
\v 4 Waxxa Idum iqqar: ‘Neccin nettwareddeǧ, \add maca\add* ad nebna řxirbat ɛawed!’, ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat: Nitni ad bnan \add ɛawed\add*, \add maca\add* Necc ad hedmeɣ u ad asen řaɣan ‘Tammurt n uɛeffan’, u \add ɛawed\add*: ‘Řgens wenni x isexxeḍ SIDI i řebda!’
\v 5 Tiṭṭawin nwem ad t ẓaren u kenniw ad tinim: ‘D ameqqran SIDI tiwa i temmurt n Israil!’”
\b
\s1 Drus n uweqqar i tqeddast n SIDI jar řgens
\m 
\v 6 “Mmis ittweqqar babas d umsexxar bab nnes. Mařa Necc aqa d Baba, mani iqqim \add xenni\add* řewqar i Necc? Mařa Necc aqa d SIDI, mani teqqim tiggʷudi nni zzayi?, iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, i kenniw, \add a\add* ikehhanen, inni isseḥqaren Isem inu. \add Maca\add* kenniw teqqarem: ‘Min zi nesseḥqar neccin Isem nnec?’
\v 7 Kenniw tᵉttawyem-dd aɣrum ixemjen x uɛalṭar inu, teqqarem: ‘Min zi i Cek nessxemmej?’ Min zi aqa kenniw teqqarem: ‘Tazewḍa n SIDI d tameḥqurt.’
\v 8 Maɣar umi kenniw tᵉttawyem min iǧan d aḍarɣař i taɣarṣt, ma war iǧi aya d řɣar? U xmi ɣa tawyem kenniw min iǧan d aqejdaḥ niɣ min iheřcen, ma war iǧi aya d řɣar! Siweḍ aya ict n twařa ɣar lwali. Ma cek ad as dd-tased x řxaḍar niɣ netta ad yiři mliḥ akidek?, iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat.”
\m 
\v 9 “\add Xenni\add* řexxu, arzum udem n Arebbi, \add ḥima\add* Netta ad xaneɣ iḥinn. \add Maca\add* man aya ittwagg zzaywem! Ma ad yiři s nneyyet tecna i yijj zzaywem?, iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat.
\v 10 Man wen zzaywem i ɣa ibellɛen \add xenni\add* tiwwura, \add ařami\add* nitni war ttesriqqin \add ɛad\add* aɛalṭar inu baṭeř. Necc war daywem ttifeɣ arḍa, iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, u \add uřa d\add* tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* zeg ufus nwem war dd-tᵉttis x řxaḍar inu. \x ◘ \xo 1:10 \xt Ica. 1:11; Irm. 6:20; Ɛam. 5:21, 22\x*
\v 11 Maɣar zi mani dd tneqqar tfuct ař mani tɣeǧi, ad yiři Yisem inu d ameqqran jar řegnus u di kuř amcan ad awyen tawhibt n řebxur i Yisem inu uřa d ict n tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add*, maɣar Isem inu d ameqqran jar řegnus, iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat.
\v 12 Maca kenniw tessɛiǧitem \add Isem nni\add* am teqqarem: ‘Tazewḍa n Sidi inu texmej u řɣiǧet nnes, \add ixs ad yini\add* macca nnes, d tameḥqurt!’
\v 13 Kenniw teqqarem \add ɛawed\add*: ‘Xzar, man\add a\add* amnus- a!’, maca kenniw \add simant nwem\add* tsuḍmem xas, iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat. Kenniw tᵉttawyem-dd min ittwacaren, u min ittqejdḥen d min iheřcen tᵉttwayem-dd am tewhibt. Ma ad ayi iɛjeb man aya zeg ufus nwem?, iqqar SIDI.
\v 14 Ittwanɛeř uɣeccac, wenni ɣar iǧa ijj n řmař d awtem di tḥimart nnes uca iwaɛd \add i-t\add* u \add xenni\add* iɣarṣ i yijj n řmař d aneɛḍub i Sidi! Maɣar Necc d ijj n Ujeǧid d ameqqran, iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, u Isem inu d ameqqran jar řegnus.”
\b
\b
\c 2
\s1 Aɛřam ɣar ikehhanen
\m 
\v 1 “Řexxu, i kenniw \add teǧa\add* tewṣiyyet-a, \add a\add* ikehhanen.
\v 2 Mařa kenniw war tesřim u war tt tkessim ɣar wuř, maḥend ad tcennɛem Isem inu, iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, \add xenni\add* necc ad ssekkeɣ nneɛřet jar awem u ad neɛřeɣ lbarakat nwem, \add wah,\add* aqa neɛřeɣ ten řexxu, minzi kenniw war tt tkessim ɣar wuř. \x ◘ \xo 2:2 \xt Lawi 26:14; Aɛwd. 28:15\x*
\v 3 Xzar, Necc ad kenniw ɛaqbeɣ di zzariɛet u ad zuzzareɣ amessař x iɣembab nwem, amessař n řeɛyudat nwem, u s man aya ad kenniw awyen ssenni.
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* ad tessnem kenniw, aqa d Necc i ɣarwem dd-issekken tawṣeyyet-a, ḥima ad tiři d Řɛahd inu ak-d Lawi, iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat.
\v 5 Řɛahd inu akides tuɣa d tudart \add u\add* d řehna. Necc wciɣ as ten ařami ɣa iggʷed netta u netta tuɣa itteggʷed zzayi u ittenexřaɛ zeg Yisem inu.
\v 6 Ccariɛa n tidett tuɣa-tt deg uqemmum nnes u war ittwif min war iseggden x iyencicen nnes. Netta yuyur akidi di řehna u di řeṣfayet u yarra aṭṭas tuben zi řmuɛṣiyyet nsen.
\v 7 Maɣar aqa ittxeṣṣa iyencicen n ukehhan ad ḥḍan tussna u zeg uqemmum nnes tᵉttwarezzu Ccariɛa, maɣar netta d amsekki n SIDI n řɛeskarat.”
\m 
\v 8 “\add Maca\add* kenniw \add maca\add* tḥeyydem x webrid, tessenqarḍem aṭṭas zi tɣuri n Ccariɛa, tareddǧem Řɛahd n Lawi, iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat.
\v 9 Uřa d Necc arriɣ kenniw tᵉttwaɛiffem u war teǧim zzat i marra řgens, minzi kenniw war teḥḍim ibriden inu u tᵉtteggem s wudmawen di tmesřact n useřmed n Ccariɛa.”
\b
\s1 SIDI icarreh aǧaf
\m 
\v 10 “Ma neccin war ɣarneɣ marra mɣir ijj n Baba? Ma war d aneɣ dd-ixřeq mɣir ijj n Arebbi? Mayemmi xenni neccin nɣeddar ijj wenneɣni, ařami nessefsad Řɛahd n řejdud nneɣ?
\v 11 Yahuda aqa iɣdar, tᵉttwagg ict n jjɛifect di Israil u di Urcalim, maɣar Yahuda issɛiǧet min iqeddsen n SIDI i ittexs Netta, maɣar Yahuda imřec yeǧis n ijj n arebbi d aɣrib. \f ◼ \fr 2:11 \fk i ittexs Netta\ft - ixs ad yini ‘Israil’ am temɣart n Arebbi nni zzayes ittwaxḍaren. Di řweqt n Malaxi tuɣa Yahuda d Israil d ijjen, minzi 10 n tqebbař n Israil war dd-dwiřent ca ɣar temmurt n Israil. Mɣir ca zzaysent dewřent-i-dd ak-d Yahuda uca zeddɣen jar ayt n Yahuda d Binyamin. Di řweqt nni tuɣa war ɣarsen teǧi tesɣart nsen n zic umi ibḍa Yacuwa tammurt n Kenɛan jar 12 iḥenjiren n Yaɛqub.\f*
\v 12 SIDI ad iteḥḥa marra wi itteggen man aya zeg iqiḍan n Yaɛqub, wi ittřaɣan d wenni dd ittarran, \add ɛad\add* uřa d wenni ittwehhben tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* i SIDI n řɛeskarat.”\f ◼ \fr 2:12 \fk ad iteḥḥa\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘ad iqḍeɛ’.\f*
\m 
\v 13 “Tamesřact wiss tnayen i tᵉtteggem, aqa kenniw teddařem aɛalṭar n SIDI s imeṭṭawen, s tɣuyyit u s sqinfet, minzi war din \add teǧi\add* ɛad teynit \add zzayes\add* i tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* u war tt iqebbeř ɛad s arḍa zeg ufus nwem.
\v 14 Kenniw teqqarem: ‘Mayemmi?’ Minzi SIDI tuɣa d ccahed jar cek d temɣart n temẓi nnec, tenni teɣdared cek, \add waxxa\add* nettat d taɛcirt nnec uřa d tamɣart n řɛahd nnec.
\v 15 Uřa d ijjen zeg wenni ɣar iǧa \add ɛad\add* buḥbeř, war iggi man aya! U min tuɣa \add igga\add* wanita? Wanita tuɣa yarezzu zzariɛet n AREBBI! S uya, ḥḍam \add x\add* buḥbeř nwem u ejj i-t war iɣeddar tamɣart n ṭemzi nnec.
\v 16 Maɣar: ‘\add Netta iqqar\add*, aqa icarh i-tt, \add uca xenni:\add* Aǧaf!’, iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, ‘\add Ammu i\add* iddař netta řɣecc s warruḍ nnes!’, inna SIDI n řɛeskarat. S uya ḥḍam x buḥbeř nwem, war ttɣeddarem ca!
\m 
\v 17 Kenniw tessahařem SIDI s wawařen nwem. Kenniw teqqarem: ‘Min zi t nessahař neccin?’ Maɣar kenniw teqqarem: ‘Qaɛ wenni itteggen řɣar, iṣbeḥ di tiṭṭawin n SIDI u nitni usin as-dd x řxaḍar!’, niɣ: ‘Mani iǧa AREBBI n řḥukm?’”
\b
\b
\c 3
\s1 Tawasit n lmalak n Řɛahd
\m 
\v 1 “Xzar, Necc ad ssekkeɣ lmalak inu inu, wenni i ɣa isswejden abrid zzat i wudem inu. Deɣya ad dd-yas ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant nnes, Sidi, wenni tarezzum kenniw, lmalak n Řɛahd, wenni \add d awem\add* dd-ittasen x řxaḍar nwem. Xzar, Netta ad dd-yas!, inna SIDI n řɛeskarat. \x ◘ \xo 3:1 \xt Mt. 11:10; Mk. 1:2; Lk. 1:76; 7:27; Ica. 40:3 \x*
\v 2 \add Maca\add* man wen i ɣa yarbun ass n twasit nnes u man wen i ɣa iqqimen ibedd, xmi i dd ɣa iban Netta? Maɣar Netta am tmessi n usefsay u am llixiyya n iɣessařen.
\v 3 Netta ad iqqim, \add am\add* wenni issefsiyyen u ittṣeffan nnuqart. Netta ad issizdig iḥenjiren n Lawi u ad ten iṣeffa am wureɣ u am nnuqart, u nitni ad wehhben ict n tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* di tsegda.
\m 
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* ad dd-tas tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* n Yahuda d Urcalim x řxaḍar n SIDI am deg wussan n zic, am deg iseggʷusa iɛdun.
\v 5 Necc ad kenniw adseɣ, ḥima ad xawem ḥekmeɣ u ad cehdeɣ s tazřa x iseḥḥaren d imzennayen u x yinni ittjaǧan ẓur u x yinni iḥeṣṣaren řmunet n ucewwař, \add u x yenni\add* iḥeṣṣaren tajjač d uyujiř u war zzayi tteggʷeden ca, iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat.”\x ◘ \xo 3:5 \xt Uf. 20:7; 22:22; Aɛwd. 24:17; Ɛam. 2:7\x*
\b
\s1 Ařaɣi i ttubet
\m 
\v 6 “Maɣar Necc, SIDI, war beddřeɣ ca u kenniw, ayt n Yaɛqub, war tefnam. \x ◘ \xo 3:6 \xt Izhd. 33:11; Awřn. 19:21; Ica. 14:26, 27; 25:9; 46:10\x*
\v 7 Zeg wussan n řejdud nwem kenniw tḥeyydem x tweṣṣa inu u kenniw war tent teḥḍim ca. Dewřem-dd ɣari, xenni ad dd ɣarwem dewřeɣ Necc, iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat. Maca kenniw teqqarem: ‘S min zi i dd ɣa nedweř?’ \x ◘ \xo 3:7 \xt Zak. 1:3\x*
\m 
\v 8 Ma izemmar bnadem ad yacar AREBBI? Aqa kenniw tᵉttacarem ayi u teqqarem: ‘S min zi Cek nettacar?’ \add Zi\add* řeɛcur d tewhibt n usgeɛɛed!
\v 9 Kenniw tᵉttwaneɛřem s yict n nneɛřet, minzi kenniw tᵉttacarem ayi, \add wah,\add* řgens marra.
\v 10 Awyem-dd marra řeɛcur deg wexxam n řexzen, maḥend ad tiři macca di Taddart inu u qeǧbem ayi zzayes, iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, ma Necc \add xenni\add* war d awem arezzmeɣ tiburjatin n ujenna u ad xawem zeǧɛeɣ lbaraka, ař din ɣa yiři ktar zi min ittwaḥdajen.
\v 11 Aburxes ad t ssiggʷedeɣ di ṭṭweɛ nwem, maḥend netta war ittjeyyeḥ ṣṣabet n wudem n temmurt nwem u maḥend tazayart deg weḥwic war tᵉttawi řɣiǧet i war yiwiḍen, inna SIDI n řɛeskarat.
\v 12 Marra řegnus ad inin: ‘D amimun i kenniw!’, maɣar kenniw ad tiřim d ict n temmurt yarḍan, iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat.”
\b
\s1 Imseggaden d lkuffar
\m 
\v 13 “Awařen nwem dewřen qesḥen xafi aṭṭas, iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat. Kenniw teqqarem: ‘Min i xak neqqar neccin?’ \x ◘ \xo 3:13 \xt Ayub 21:14, 15\x*
\v 14 Kenniw teqqarem: ‘Aqa baṭeř i nettsexxar i AREBBI, maɣar man řefḍeř i zi neḥḍa tasexxart nnes u aqa nuyur \add deg werruḍ\add* abarcan zzat i wudem n SIDI n řɛeskarat?
\v 15 Xenni řexxu, nḥesseb ayt nnfaxet d amimun. Ɛad inni itteggen taɛeffant, ttwabennan. Nitni ttjarraben \add ɛad\add* AREBBI, \add waxxa amenni\add* nejjmen.’
\v 16 Xenni inni itteggʷeden SIDI mmsawařan \add ammu\add*: ‘SIDI ittarra taynit u ittesřa. Ad ittwari ijj n wedlis n řidaret zzat i wudem nnes, di ṭṭweɛ n yinni itteggʷeden SIDI u ttidaren Isem nnes.’
\v 17 Nitni ad iřin Nnec, iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, deg wass i ɣa ggeɣ u Necc ad ten ssɛizzeɣ am issɛizz ijj n weryaz mmis nni i d as ittsexxaren.
\v 18 Xenni kenniw ad tẓarem ɛawed řfarq jar umsegged d wenni itteggen tuɛeffna, jar wenni ittsexxaren i AREBBI d wenni i war d as ittsexxaren.”
\m 
\v 19 “Maɣar xzar, ass nni ad dd-yas, yareqq am tefqunt. \add Xenni\add* marra ayt n nnfaxet d iɛeffanen ad iřin am uřum uca ass i dd ɣa yasen ad ten issareɣ, iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat. \add Ass nni\add* war ittejji weẓwar uřa d taseṭṭa. \x ◘ \xo 3:19 \xt Yuw. 2:10, 31; 3:15; Ica. 13:6-13; 24:23; Am. 8:9; Mt. 24:29; Řex. 2:20; Asa. 6:12-13\x*
\v 20 I kenniw \add maca\add*, inni itteggʷeden Isem inu, ad dd-tenqar tfuct n tsegda u ad yiři ugenfu sadu wafriwen nnes u kenniw ad teffɣem u ad teggem ineggizen n řefraḥet am yiɛejmiyyen \add i dd-yusin\add* zi řkuri. \f ◼ \fr 3:20 \fk iɛejmiyyen\ft - niɣ ‘amwa’, ‘ayenduz’ niɣ ‘yuggu’.\f*
\v 21 Kenniw ad tɛefsem x iɛeffanen, minzi nitni ad dewřen d iɣɣeḍ sadu tisi n iḍaren nwem, deg wass nni i ɣa ggeɣ Necc, iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat.”
\b
\m 
\v 22 Xemmem ɣar Ccariɛa n Musa, amsexxar inu, tenni i d as umureɣ deg \add wedrar n\add* Hurib x marra Israil, tiweṣṣa d lfarayiḍ.\x ◘ \xo 3:22 \xt Aɛwd. 6:3\x*
\m 
\v 23 Xzar, Necc ad awem dd-ssekkeɣ anabi Iliya, qbeř dd ɣa yas wass ameqqran d issiggʷiden n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 3:23 \xt Mt. 11:14; 17:11, 12, 13; Mk. 9:11, 12, 13; Lk. 1:7\x*
\v 24 Netta ad yarr uř n ibabaten ɣar iḥenjiren \add nsen\add* d wuř n iḥenjiren ɣar ibabaten nsen, maḥend Necc war dd- ttiseɣ u ad ḥarrmeɣ tammurt qaɛ \add i uteḥḥi\add*.” 
